response.overview: In Chicazo, Luna Corazón plays a gorgeous, hot and somehow absent stripper from a peep show down Las Ramblas, in Barcelona. She’s the one who shows up when Tyler Nixon – a sweet, regular traveler – walks in with a couple of coins in his hand. He doesn’t know what to expect. She knows exactly what to do. With spectacular Finnish tango as a soundtrack, she’ll expose herself entirely for this show – only to dress herself again once it’s all over.
response.title: Chicazo
